data.description: Great corner lot near Little Rock Air Force Base! Open floor plan with lots of natural light and a large bar for cooking and/or entertaining. The multi-purpose room at the back of the living area has served as an office, guest accommodations, and a playroom.  Guest bath has an oversized floor level entry shower. The storage area in the back does have electric and could be included into the home to add another room. Within minutes of LRAFB, 67/167, and the local JNPSD schools. FHA assumable loan with a low 2.8% rate!
